366
00:23:51,180 --> 00:23:52,222
Hey, Jin Seung-hee.

367
00:23:55,059 --> 00:23:56,226
Do you not believe me?

368
00:24:00,856 --> 00:24:01,857
Do you not…

369
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:06,612
