who wants to be in politics?

456
00:30:13,687 --> 00:30:14,771
Do you regret it?

457
00:30:23,655 --> 00:30:24,489
<i><font color="white">Yes.</font></i>

458
00:30:25,574 --> 00:30:26,491
<i><font color="white">I do.</font></i>

459
00:30:28,076 --> 00:30:30,287
<i><font color="white">But as for falling in love with you…</font></i>

460
00:30:31,997 --> 00:30:33,123
I don't regret it.

461
00:30:33,874 --> 00:30:34,958
Never.

462
00:30:44,468 --> 00:30:45,802
Thank you, Hye-joo.

463
00:31:19,753 --> 00:31:20,754
You.

464
00:31:28,011 --> 00:31:29,262
Can you take responsibility?

465
00:31:35,227 --> 00:31:37,104
You're one to talk.

466
00:32:00,252 --> 00:32:01,711
