467
00:32:01,795 --> 00:32:02,754
Yes.

468
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:04,923
And you?

469
00:32:05,841 --> 00:32:07,676
-Yes.
-Are you going to a funeral?

470
00:32:08,885 --> 00:32:11,596
