for the rest of her life.

694
00:51:12,778 --> 00:51:14,947
I need to know what happened in her past

695
00:51:15,030 --> 00:51:16,949
to be able to protect her

696
00:51:17,032 --> 00:51:18,701
from whatever might happen.

697
00:51:21,078 --> 00:51:23,080
So please tell me. I ask of you.

698
00:51:28,711 --> 00:51:31,797
It's related to someone
named Jin Seung-hee, right?

699
00:51:33,632 --> 00:51:34,883
Jae-eun…

700
00:51:36,302 --> 00:51:38,053
mentioned her?

701
00:51:38,137 --> 00:51:40,014
Yes, just the name.

702
00:51:48,188 --> 00:51:50,232
There was this boy

703
00:51:50,816 --> 00:51:52,443
who was accepted into
the SNU School of Law

704
00:51:53,110 --> 00:51:54,862
for the first time from Youngsan High.

705
00:51:56,196 --> 00:51:58,615
<i><font color="white">Okay. I'll be there by 3:30 p.m.</font></i>

706
00:52:24,475 --> 00:52:26,018
HERE LIES JUNG SU-HYEON

707
00:52:26,101 --> 00:52:28,354
You know that
Su-hyeon was a stubborn girl, right?

708
00:52:30,230 --> 00:52:31,273
Yes.

709
00:52:31,940 --> 00:52:35,861
That persistence was something
that kept her going since childhood.

710
00:52:36,904 --> 00:52:38,697
I couldn't believe she even had cancer,

711
00:52:39,281 --> 00:52:41,325
but she also refused treatment
because she was pregnant.

712
00:52:41,408 --> 00:52:45,788
I did everything I could to convince her
that she could always have another child,

713
00:52:45,871 --> 00:52:47,748
but she just wouldn't listen.

714
00:52:48,374 --> 00:52:49,625
After Ji-hoon was born,

715
00:52:50,209 --> 00:52:51,919
she didn't last a year, did she?

716
00:52:54,088 --> 00:52:55,130
No.

717
00:52:55,839 --> 00:53:00,469
To be honest, back then,
I blamed you more than her.

718
00:53:01,136 --> 00:53:03,847
But having thought about it
after she passed,

719
00:53:03,931 --> 00:53:07,184
I realized that her decision
must have been tougher for you.

720
00:53:08,394 --> 00:53:09,436
Right?

721
00:53:12,398 --> 00:53:16,944
So I thought I would be fine
as long as Ji-hoon lived a good life.

722
00:53:18,320 --> 00:53:19,947
And even though I didn't see him often,

723
00:53:20,531 --> 00:53:22,950
I figured he was doing well

724
00:53:23,033 --> 00:53:24,743
with his dad, stepmom, and sister.

725
00:53:26,286 --> 00:53:28,872
But I kept seeing him on the news
for being up to no good.

726
00:53:31,375 --> 00:53:32,709
I never thought he'd go like this.

727
00:53:36,380 --> 00:53:37,798
It's all my fault.

728
00:53:39,049 --> 00:53:40,259
I'm sorry.

729
00:53:43,804 --> 00:53:47,433
You can stop sending us holiday gifts.

730
00:53:48,016 --> 00:53:49,184
There's no need.

731
00:53:50,144 --> 00:53:53,230
You only got to live with her
for less than two years,

732
00:53:53,313 --> 00:53:55,774
yet you've cared for us
for the past 20 years.

733
00:53:56,900 --> 00:53:58,694
I'm saying we should cut our ties.

734
00:54:00,737 --> 00:54:03,323
We don't have to see each other
unless there's bad news.

735
00:54:04,575 --> 00:54:06,034
We won't ask much of you.

736
00:54:06,118 --> 00:54:07,870
Just forget all about us

737
00:54:09,163 --> 00:54:10,831
and do good work for the country.

738
00:54:21,300 --> 00:54:22,509
Eat with us before you go.

739
00:54:23,093 --> 00:54:24,136
Yes, I will.

740
00:54:39,568 --> 00:54:41,653
YOUNGSAN MIDDLE SCHOOL
YOUNGSAN HIGH SCHOOL

741
00:56:21,044 --> 00:56:22,588
My mom will be here soon.

742
00:56:24,881 --> 00:56:26,883
Your phone was off.

743
00:56:27,718 --> 00:56:29,636
I called in case you changed your mind.

744
00:56:30,554 --> 00:56:32,222
But you found your way here.

745
00:56:35,058 --> 00:56:36,768
I used to come here often.

746
00:56:41,607 --> 00:56:43,442
The house hasn't changed at all, has it?

747
00:56:45,736 --> 00:56:47,029
It's the same

748
00:56:48,238 --> 00:56:49,656
as it was 20 years ago.

749
00:57:09,635 --> 00:57:10,844
Go wash your face.

750
00:57:12,262 --> 00:57:14,014
And wipe your tears off.

751
00:57:15,015 --> 00:57:19,019
Don't you dare try to make
my mom feel sorry for you.

752
00:57:20,062 --> 00:57:21,021
You got that?

753
00:57:58,976 --> 00:58:00,644
Seung-hee, what's wrong?

754
00:58:24,710 --> 00:58:26,753
Ms. Jin, open the door right now.

755
00:58:27,713 --> 00:58:28,755
Now!

756
00:59:00,579 --> 00:59:03,457
TROLLEY

757
00:59:03,540 --> 00:59:04,624
<i><font color="white">Just stay put for now.</font></i>

758
00:59:04,708 --> 00:59:06,960
<i><font color="white">Nam Joong-do will retaliate.</font></i>

759
00:59:07,044 --> 00:59:08,962
I'll get on my knees
and do anything you ask.

760
00:59:09,046 --> 00:59:12,174
Don't resent me for the things
I do from this point on.

761
00:59:12,257 --> 00:59:14,176
<i><font color="white">-Ms. Kim should have stayed out of it.
-What are you doing?</font></i>

762
00:59:14,926 --> 00:59:16,553
<i><font color="white">Please don't go into my room
when I'm not here.</font></i>

763
00:59:16,636 --> 00:59:20,640
<i><font color="white">This could complicate things for you
with the election coming up, right?</font></i>

764
00:59:20,724 --> 00:59:23,393
You don't have to do anything
or worry about anything.

765
00:59:23,477 --> 00:59:25,520
<i><font color="white">If you mess with her
or hurt her in any way,</font></i>

766
00:59:25,604 --> 00:59:27,189
<i><font color="white">you won't be able to
handle the consequences.</font></i>

767
00:59:27,272 --> 00:59:29,733
<i><font color="white">Why is it happening all over again?</font></i>

768
00:59:29,816 --> 00:59:31,485
<i><font color="white">I'm Assemblyman Nam Joong-do of Sinyang.</font></i>

769
00:59:31,568 --> 00:59:33,779
<i><font color="white">I'll take responsibility for everything.</font></i>

770
00:59:34,571 --> 00:59:39,451
